### Description

When I start my Angular 7 application using `ng serve`, and go to the webpage at localhost:4200 in Internet Explorer 11 in compatibility mode, I am seeing this error:

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13770435/60520210-fdf03380-9cb2-11e9-828d-35df9a456dea.png)

## üåç  Your Environment

**Angular Version:** 7.2.15
**Internet Explorer version:** IE 11.3024.14393.0

